com.snapon.sbs.dns.emailsettings

Class EmailJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snapon.sbs.dns.emailsettings.EmailJob
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.alisonassociates.npd.workflowmanager.Job, Comparable<com.alisonassociates.npd.workflowmanager.Job>

    public class EmailJob
extends Object
implements com.alisonassociates.npd.workflowmanager.Job
    This class represents an entry made into the EMAIL_JOB table. There should be only one job per email request sent to the mailer so it will be the mailers job to ensure a job entry is correctly added.
